{"tid":1694833,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周同學腦幹死亡 哦 香港人聽日繼續翻工","createTime":"2019-11-05T10:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T10:15:52.000Z","uid":259345,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc68126d4a18a37cfee2c7315c29dc607e93340","tid":1694833,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:01:48.000Z","msg":"好嬲阿 有手足跌咗落黎腦幹死亡<br />\n出去拖下手 唱下歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你地瞓醒未？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n場運動已經開始衰落緊 每個星期六日出完黎 比人拉咗幾百個然後又<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續翻工？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>今日終於有手足腦幹死亡，姐係同死咗無分別 </strong></span></span><br />\n人地叻仔黎 大好前途 為咗我地呢班<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連無限期罷工都唔敢既垃圾，犧牲晒佢有既一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n算喇 我都睇死大家唔會罷工唔會罷課架喇<br />\n由佢地白死囉<br />\n由香港步向滅亡囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果唔想咁既 比翻啲行動得唔得阿香港人？</span></strong></span><br />\n我無咁既能力去號召大家聽日後日又可能今晚做啲咩<br />\n你地應該自己思考咩去做咩行動<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港 時代革命<br />\n#唔係遊戲黎"},{"pid":"d55f98fbd539c5a7c65cd6975087c52f690d0223","tid":1694833,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:03:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 認輸</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679167aa052a666373034338675b709856c38512","tid":1694833,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"算喇呢啲垃圾post<br />\n無香港人會睇"},{"pid":"aa9481d73d2e9098b396abb1bab3f64f8e0642e1","tid":1694833,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,